title: 10 Reasons We Might Never Be Able to Colonize Space

media:group.media:title: 10 Reasons We Might Never Be Able to Colonize Space
media:group.media:description:
Colonizing space is a romantic fantasy that we've dreamed about for hundreds, if not thousands of years. Although we edge closer with each passing year, there are still many obstacles that we aren't sure how to overcome to make that "mission to mars" a reality.
